---
title: Caprese Style Salad and Pesto Dressing with Roast Potatoes, Ciabatta Croutons and Baby Plum Tomatoes
description: Welcome the sunshine with our summery Caprese Style Mozzarella Salad and Pesto Dressing. Filled with a taste of Italian sun, this salad is perfect for a lighter evening meal or to accompany a BBQ.
